    "description": "Lily was a normal student. She attends St. Ludmilla’s Academy with her friends. She never thought she would wake up one day in <i>The Ritual</i>. What is <i>The Ritual</i>? She needs to find out. <br><br>Lily and Taro are separated from the rest of their group, and they must find their way back. Did the others even survive? <br><br>Set in a prestigious boarding school, you must navigate through the winding hallowed halls of St. Ludmilla’s Academy that has become your prison. Who is your captor? You must hide from the evils of the school that was so perfectly concealed for all this time. How was it concealed? While dodging and running from the evils St. Ludmilla’s has to offer, you find clues and unravel the mystery of <i>The Ritual</i>.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037170/extras/e324df62b025a171e74b919cea7502bd.poster.avif?t=1718786180\" width=692 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037170/extras/e324df62b025a171e74b919cea7502bd.webm?t=1718786180\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037170/extras/e324df62b025a171e74b919cea7502bd.mp4?t=1718786180\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You must run and hide from the creatures that seemed to have crawled out from the depths of hell. Dodge the monsters, or you <strong>WILL</strong> be their next meal.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037170/extras/731a404919c8722a105b18e39cf3c3da.poster.avif?t=1718786180\" width=662 height=372 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037170/extras/731a404919c8722a105b18e39cf3c3da.webm?t=1718786180\" type=\"video/webm; c